  slug="intersection-observer-api"
  title="The IntersectionObserver API: lazy-loading and scroll effects"
  description="Use IntersectionObserver to lazy-load images, reveal elements on scroll and build infinite scroll — with threshold and rootMargin explained, plus runnable examples."
  cat="apis"
  day={10}
